           SPELL=foomatic
         VERSION=2.0-current
          SOURCE=$SPELL-$VERSION.tar.gz
SOURCE_DIRECTORY=$BUILD_DIRECTORY/$SPELL-$VERSION
   SOURCE_URL[0]=http://www.linuxprinting.org/download/foomatic/$SOURCE
        WEB_SITE=http://www.linuxprinting.org/foomatic.html
      LICENSE[0]=GPL
         ENTERED=20020405
         UPDATED=20020420
      MAINTAINER=djcomputer@gmx.net
           SHORT="Foomatic printing system"
cat << EOF

Foomatic is a system for using free software printer drivers with common
spoolers on Unix.  It supports LPD, PDQ, CUPS, the VA Linux LPD, LPRng, PPR,
and direct spooler-less printing and any free software driver for which
execution data has been entered in the database.

EOF
